VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY: Required for OpenRouter API calls.
Create your key in OpenRouter dashboard and paste it here.
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY="MY_OPENROUTER_API_KEY"

VITE_OPENROUTER_MODEL: Optional model id from OpenRouter.
VITE_OPENROUTER_MODEL="mistralai/mistral-small-3.2-24b-instruct"

VITE_APP_URL: The URL where this applet is hosted.
Used for self-referential links, OAuth callbacks, and API endpoints.
VITE_APP_URL="https://researc.netlify.app"

VITE_API_BASE_URL: Set this to your Netlify site URL for production (e.g., https://researc.netlify.app).
Leave empty for local development.
VITE_API_BASE_URL="https://researc.netlify.app"